## Token: $COOP

$COOP is the platform's own token, earned through participation (eggs) and distributed via airdrop.

**Positioning:** $COOP is the egg that hatched the coop itself. Holding $COOP means you are part of the coop's structure — not just visiting to buy other eggs.

**Do not over-promise on $COOP utility before it is built.** Communicate: eggs now, airdrop when announced, utility to follow. Chickens are patient when the coop is good.

